{"tid":1383101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《勿忘初衷》香港人的願望","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:35:20.000Z","uid":186048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7197ffac0b96543b3ed9e12e31ebe436f4bd94a6","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">第一次開po 屌細力啲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依一兩個月 發左好多場惡夢<br />\n再每日花時間睇新聞連登tg<br />\n有啲感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由政府想強行將送中送上二讀開始<br />\n一百零三萬 到二百萬零一人上街遊行<br />\n大家都好齊心<br />\n去到近排 兄弟姊妹各自爬山<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇發現 近排既熱門 <br />\n大部分都係講點樣提升裝備<br />\n點樣對付班癲狗 <br />\n<br />\n近排每次爬山之後 就係開始暴狗開槍放煙<br />\n其實大家有冇發現<br />\n香港人開始習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且慢慢將視線轉移到黑狗<br />\n原本既初衷慢慢被遺忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重新五大訴求<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n撤回612暴動定性<br />\n<br />\n必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴<br />\n<br />\n全面落實雙真普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Be Water<br />\n</span></span><br />\n望到每次爬山後有人受傷都好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位手足 要繼續保護自己保護身邊兄弟姊妹<br />\n<br />\n有仇不報非君子 黑狗之仇<br />\n只係時間性問題 就算香港人係善忘<br />\n都唔會忘記黑狗點樣對待香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">講到1999對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c7fd2eb1ca982d57cafc62b2c90eb2e65761e042","tid":1383101,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=284609bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b1e2f0a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/</a>"},{"pid":"6844301b308159d8b4e4039648433acfe343210f","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔想再見到有手足受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個也不能少！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"75f5f387340ff26c4dfc9a8deb32b0f321f5f0af","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1e56c3f8cb21907470214d93192e9eb173291eb","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73dfcb42242c4fdffa90c642f1e3cc209d262195","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7599fa0435906c4c69cf26b3e4c67fec9a8cd7f","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1b5209bafea0509ee4869ae2f064fae38e756f6","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc62cbaed3c880e0d8ba9ef0e9c1cbd1f9413847","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以入嚟睇睇....."},{"pid":"a1bddd099276081d3f4ed4a4d41be47003536a6c","tid":1383101,"uid":186048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:35:2